Your Discord Bot Token

DISCORD_TOKEN=your_discord_bot_token_here

The ID of the channel you want the bot to scrape for history (e.g., #help)

You get this by right-clicking the channel in Discord and clicking "Copy Channel ID"

HELP_CHANNEL_ID=your_help_channel_id_here

Supabase Credentials

SUPABASE_URL=your_supabase_project_url_here
SUPABASE_KEY=your_supabase_anon_public_key_here

Google Gemini API Key

GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here